org.semanticweb.kaon2.api.logic
Interface PredicateSymbol

All Superinterfaces:
Entity, Predicate
public interface PredicateSymbol
extends Predicate, Entity

Represents a predicate in a program which does not come from an OWL knowledge base.

Method Detail

getName

java.lang.String getName()
Returns the name of the predicate symbol. The short name is equal to the URI. This method exists purely to make this interface symmetric with FunctionSymbol.

Returns:
the name of the predicate symbol

getFullName

java.lang.String getFullName()
Returns the full name of the predicate symbol. The full name has the form name/arity.

Returns:
the full name of the predicate symbol
